Subject: Reports are not generating after upgrade
Description: Hi Team, We are facing some issues with the reports, there's this error where the system error is showing 'Unexpected exception: Encountered Error: 'Reports.xml has not been transformed at drive: " while generating report Kindly assign someone to troubleshoot this with us on this, thank you.
What_We_Know__c:
When we clicked on reports, we saw this error message:

'Unexpected exception: Encountered error: Reports.xml has not been transformed at F:Program FilesSTEALTHbitsStealthAUDITReports."


To resolve this issue, we navigated to the above directory, made a backup of reports.xml and then deleted the file from parent folder. After that we re-launched the NEA console, and we were able to view reports.
Next_Steps__c: Customer will update us by end of the day. I will follow up with them next week if no response received.
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
When you tried to view reports in the NEA console, you were observing an error message: 'Unexpected exception: Encountered error: Reports.xml has not been transformed at F:Program FilesSTEALTHbitsStealthAUDITReports.'

Resolution
To resolve this issue, we navigated to the above directory, made a backup of reports.xml and then deleted the file from parent folder. After that we re-launched the NEA console, and we were able to view reports.
